Mixin to setup fake models for tests.

Usage - the model:

    class FakeModel(models.Model, TestMixin):
        _name = 'fake.model'

        name = fields.Char()

Usage - the test klass:

    @classmethod
    def setUpClass(cls):
        super().setUpClass()
        FakeModel._test_setup_model(cls.env)

    @classmethod
    def tearDownClass(cls):
        FakeModel._test_teardown_model(cls.env)
        super().tearDownClass()
